{"tid":2279088,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陶傑：拜登當選後，CNN 評論員Van Jones 哽咽：我終於能教好我的兒子","createTime":"2020-11-09T14:05:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T14:16:57.000Z","uid":22575,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3b21970a7db8fffb348abff98c7c0fb2450c154f","tid":2279088,"uid":22575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T14:05:06.000Z","msg":"在拜登宣佈確定當選後，CNN 時事評論員范瓊斯（Van Jones）在節目上分析論述，講到激動處，突然哽咽，說：「身為父親，現在我鬆了一口氣，我終於可以告訴我的孩子：品行是重要的、是有意義的，誠實是重要的，做一個好人也是重要的。」<br />\n<br />\n暗指過去川普的行徑，難以令人家長說服、教育小孩。這段畫面曝光後，吸引不少網友目光，更在社群網站上瘋傳。<br />\n<br />\n如果只選一個能令家長教子女的人做總統，以後美國總統候選人最好由幼稚園教師此一組別初選。<br />\n<br />\n政客和律師，都是好人？即將上任的這位總統，都具有這兩重身份。<br />\n<br />\nCome on man, you can do better.<br />\n<br />\n以這位主持人的標準：民主黨前總統克林頓與女助理萊溫斯基，動用雪茄做性侵犯的工具，在國會接受問話，繪聲繪色，請問克林頓是不是教好子女的好人典型？<br />\n<br />\n川普的兒子最少沒有吸毒，川普的女兒貴氣，沒有紋身性濫交。<br />\n<br />\n當左派仇恨川普，他們說：川普無法令我如何教好孩子。<br />\n<br />\n但當拜登被揭發並沒有教好兒子，他們說：兒子作風即使敗壞，跟父親沒有關係。<br />\n<br />\n在中國歷史上，曹操是好人還是壞人？曾國藩是好人還是壞人？蔣介石是好人還是壞人？<br />\n<br />\n但這種名嘴，是沒有這種知識邏輯的。他們憑一句話，再在電視鏡頭前抹眼淚，就將許多頭腦簡單的人也跟着大愛感動，點頭說：對對對。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/272574169481780/posts/4592983614107459/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F272574169481780%2Fposts%2F4592983614107459%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y0Ka%2BtsrA1nil%2BMmquCK26s%3D&h=11737cd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/272574169481780/posts/4592983614107459/?d=n</a> <br />\n<br />\n影片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2020/11/07/opinions/the-election-is-a-huge-relief-van-jones/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2020%2F11%2F07%2Fopinions%2Fthe-election-is-a-huge-relief-van-jones%2Findex.html&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y0Ka%2BtsrA1nil%2BMmquCK26s%3D&h=f2da1eca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2020%2F11%2F07%2Fopinions%2Fthe-election-is-a-huge-relief-van-jones%2Findex.html&h=ec5cfd23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/2020/11/07/opinions/the-election-is-a-huge-relief-van-jones/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"9b314bc1d57eab0cffe3809839423311783ea6d9","tid":2279088,"uid":291465,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T14:16:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-tpe1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/124366883_360092381944647_6126134460536222540_n.jpg?_nc_cat=111&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=dbeb18&amp;_nc_ohc=sIS41UvGTN8AX9EzgUi&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-tpe1-1.xx&amp;oh=2161dedc092436227ef0391d1bf13b91&amp;oe=5FCF9845\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-tpe1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F124366883_360092381944647_6126134460536222540_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D111%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3Ddbeb18%26_nc_ohc%3DsIS41UvGTN8AX9EzgUi%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-tpe1-1.xx%26oh%3D2161dedc092436227ef0391d1bf13b91%26oe%3D5FCF9845&h=02779f27&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}